[Name] ACPI Event Daemon
[Summary] A daemon for delivering ACPI events.
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] ACPID is a completely flexible and expandable mechanism for delivering ACPI
events from the kernel to user-space. It can be configured to perform any
action at all when events occur, through regex matches and arbitrary action
rules.
[Homepage] http://acpid.sourceforge.net/
